## Additional Terms for DIGIY PAY

### Brand & Trademark
The DIGIY name, logo, and brand are trademarks of DIGIYLYFE.
While you can freely use this code, please respect our brand identity.

### 0% Commission Philosophy
If you fork this project, we encourage you to maintain the 0% commission
philosophy. The goal is to empower professionals, not extract from them.

### Attribution
If you use DIGIY PAY in your project, we'd appreciate attribution:
"Powered by DIGIY PAY" with a link to https://github.com/beauville/digiy-pay

### Support the Vision
DIGIY PAY exists to liberate African entrepreneurs from predatory commissions.
